{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "f315f5be-8e60-428f-ae88-04d75011b292",
    "name": "ZiCharge Merchant API",
    "description": "Postman collection for the ZiCharge Merchant Payment Gateway.\n\n**Flows**\n- **Deposit** — Collect payment from a customer wallet: Initiate Payment → customer pays → IPN callback → Validate Payment\n- **Withdrawal** — Push cashback/refund from merchant wallet to customer: Cashback → Validate Payment\n- **Security** — Generate API key + webhook secret for signed IPNs and keyless cashback auth\n\n**Response envelope** (all endpoints)\n```\n{ \"code\": <int>, \"messages\": [\"...\"], \"data\": { ... } | null }\n```\n`code` mirrors the logical status (200 success · 422 business/validation error · 404 not found). The HTTP status is always **200 OK**.\n\n**IPN Security** — ZiCharge signs every outbound IPN with `X-ZiCharge-Signature: t=<epoch>,v1=<hmac>`. Verify the HMAC using your `webhook_secret` and reject requests where `|now - t| > 300s`.\n\n**Setup — set these collection variables before use**\n| Variable | Example | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `base_url` | `https://dev.zicharge.com` | Use `https://secure.zicharge.com` for production |\n| `merchant_mobile_no` | `+9647712345678` | Provisioned merchant wallet number (E.164) |\n| `store_password` | `your-store-password` | Provisioned store password — never expose client-side |\n| `api_key` | *(from generate-api-key)* | API key for cashback auth — use `Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}` |\n| `ipn_url` | `https://yoursite.com/webhooks/zicharge/ipn` | Publicly reachable HTTPS IPN listener |\n| `order_id` | `ORD-2026-000001` | Your unique order / reference ID |\n| `customer_mobile_no` | `+9647701234567` | Customer ZiCharge wallet number (E.164) |",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "2048354"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Deposit",
      "description": "Collect payments from customer ZiCharge wallets.\n\n**Flow:** Initiate Payment (get token) → redirect customer to `payment_url` or display QR → receive IPN callback → Validate Payment to independently confirm.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Initiate Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"{{merchant_mobile_no}}\",\n  \"store_password\": \"{{store_password}}\",\n  \"order_id\": \"{{order_id}}\",\n  \"bill_amount\": 1000,\n  \"success_url\": \"https://yoursite.com/payment/success\",\n  \"cancel_url\": \"https://yoursite.com/payment/cancel\",\n  \"fail_url\": \"https://yoursite.com/payment/fail\",\n  \"customer_mobile_no\": \"{{customer_mobile_no}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/generate-payment-token",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["merchant", "generate-payment-token"]
            },
            "description": "Mint a single-use payment token and checkout URL.\n\nRedirect the customer to `payment_url` (web) or display it as a QR code (mobile). The token expires in `expires_in_minutes` minutes.\n\nAlso available at the alias `/merchant/generate-qr-token`."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Success — token minted",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\",\n  \"bill_amount\": 1000,\n  \"success_url\": \"https://yoursite.com/payment/success\",\n  \"cancel_url\": \"https://yoursite.com/payment/cancel\",\n  \"fail_url\": \"https://yoursite.com/payment/fail\",\n  \"customer_mobile_no\": \"+9647701234567\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/generate-payment-token",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "generate-payment-token"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [],\n  \"data\": {\n    \"token\": \"PMTKN7X2K9Q\",\n    \"payment_url\": \"https://dev.zicharge.com/merchant/payment?token=PMTKN7X2K9Q\",\n    \"expires_in_minutes\": 15\n  },\n  \"code\": 200\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Invalid store credentials",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"wrong-password\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\",\n  \"bill_amount\": 1000\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/generate-payment-token",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "generate-payment-token"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"Invalid store credentials.\"],\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"code\": 422\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Merchant account inactive",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\",\n  \"bill_amount\": 1000\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/generate-payment-token",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "generate-payment-token"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"Account is inactive.\"],\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"code\": 422\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Validation error — missing required field",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/generate-payment-token",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "generate-payment-token"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"merchant_mobile_no must not be blank\", \"bill_amount must not be null\"],\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"code\": 422\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "IPN Callback (Incoming — reference only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"
              },
              {
                "key": "X-ZiCharge-Signature",
                "value": "t=1716285600,v1=a3f8e2c1...<hex-hmac>",
                "description": "Stripe-style HMAC-SHA256 signature. Present only when merchant has a webhook_secret provisioned. Verify: signed_payload = t + '.' + body; expected = HMAC-SHA256(webhook_secret, signed_payload). Reject if |now - t| > 300s."
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "urlencoded",
              "urlencoded": [
                {
                  "key": "transaction_id",
                  "value": "5367827",
                  "description": "Numeric internal transaction ID (legacy field)."
                },
                {
                  "key": "tx_unique_id",
                  "value": "CVIBAON916",
                  "description": "Public transaction reference (preferred for reconciliation)."
                },
                {
                  "key": "order_id",
                  "value": "ORD-2026-000001",
                  "description": "Your order ID as submitted to Initiate Payment."
                },
                {
                  "key": "bill_amount",
                  "value": "1000.00",
                  "description": "Amount in IQD as decimal string."
                },
                {
                  "key": "customer_account_no",
                  "value": "+9647701234567",
                  "description": "Customer's ZiCharge wallet number."
                },
                {
                  "key": "status",
                  "value": "Success",
                  "description": "Transaction status: Success or Cancelled."
                },
                {
                  "key": "received_at",
                  "value": "2026-05-20 10:00:00",
                  "description": "Transaction timestamp (yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss)."
                },
                {
                  "key": "ipn",
                  "value": "1",
                  "description": "Always 1 — IPN push indicator."
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{ipn_url}}",
              "host": ["{{ipn_url}}"]
            },
            "description": "**ZiCharge → Your server.** This POST is dispatched by ZiCharge to your `ipn_url` after a payment completes or is cancelled.\n\nThis request is **reference only** — use it to simulate an IPN delivery against your local listener during development.\n\n**Your listener must:**\n1. Verify `order_id` belongs to your system before trusting the payload\n2. Mark the order as paid **only** when `status == \"Success\"`\n3. Return HTTP 200 OK — any other status is treated as a delivery failure and may be retried\n\n**Fields:** `tx_unique_id` is the public transaction reference (preferred). `transaction_id` is a legacy numeric internal ID. Correlate primarily on `order_id` + `tx_unique_id`."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "IPN Success — payment completed",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"}],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "urlencoded",
                  "urlencoded": [
                    {"key": "transaction_id", "value": "5367827"},
                    {"key": "tx_unique_id", "value": "CVIBAON916"},
                    {"key": "order_id", "value": "ORD-2026-000001"},
                    {"key": "bill_amount", "value": "1000.00"},
                    {"key": "customer_account_no", "value": "+9647701234567"},
                    {"key": "status", "value": "Success"},
                    {"key": "received_at", "value": "2026-05-20 10:00:00"},
                    {"key": "ipn", "value": "1"}
                  ]
                },
                "url": {"raw": "{{ipn_url}}", "host": ["{{ipn_url}}"]}
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "text",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/plain"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "OK"
            },
            {
              "name": "IPN Cancel — payment cancelled",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded"}],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "urlencoded",
                  "urlencoded": [
                    {"key": "transaction_id", "value": ""},
                    {"key": "tx_unique_id", "value": ""},
                    {"key": "order_id", "value": "ORD-2026-000001"},
                    {"key": "bill_amount", "value": "1000.00"},
                    {"key": "customer_account_no", "value": "+9647701234567"},
                    {"key": "status", "value": "Cancelled"},
                    {"key": "received_at", "value": "2026-05-20 10:05:00"},
                    {"key": "ipn", "value": "1"}
                  ]
                },
                "url": {"raw": "{{ipn_url}}", "host": ["{{ipn_url}}"]}
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "text",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/plain"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "OK"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Validate Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"{{merchant_mobile_no}}\",\n  \"store_password\": \"{{store_password}}\",\n  \"order_id\": \"{{order_id}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/payment/validation",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["merchant", "payment", "validation"]
            },
            "description": "Confirm a deposit transaction by `order_id`. Call this after receiving a successful IPN callback to independently verify the payment server-side.\n\nThis endpoint is read-only and safe to call multiple times.\n\nAlso available as `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` and at the alias `/merchant/validate-payment`."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Success — payment confirmed",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/payment/validation",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "payment", "validation"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"Please find your transaction details.\"],\n  \"data\": {\n    \"tx_unique_id\": \"CVIBAON916\",\n    \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\",\n    \"bill_amount\": 1000,\n    \"customer_account_no\": \"+9647701234567\",\n    \"status\": \"Success\",\n    \"received_at\": \"2026-05-20 10:00:00\"\n  },\n  \"code\": 200\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Invalid store credentials",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"wrong\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/payment/validation",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "payment", "validation"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"Invalid store credentials.\"],\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"code\": 422\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "404 Transaction not found",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-DOES-NOT-EXIST\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/payment/validation",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "payment", "validation"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"Transaction not found.\"],\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"code\": 404\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "200 Found — transaction cancelled",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\",\n  \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/merchant/payment/validation",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["merchant", "payment", "validation"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"Please find your transaction details.\"],\n  \"data\": {\n    \"tx_unique_id\": \"CVIBAON916\",\n    \"order_id\": \"ORD-2026-000001\",\n    \"bill_amount\": 1000,\n    \"customer_account_no\": \"+9647701234567\",\n    \"status\": \"Cancelled\",\n    \"received_at\": \"2026-05-20 10:05:00\"\n  },\n  \"code\": 200\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Withdrawal",
      "description": "Push credits from your merchant wallet to a customer ZiCharge personal wallet.\n\n**Flow:** Cashback (initiate transfer, settled synchronously) → Validate Payment (confirm the record).\n\n**Recommended auth:** Generate an API key first, then use `Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}` on the Cashback request.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Generate API Key",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
              {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"{{merchant_mobile_no}}\",\n  \"store_password\": \"{{store_password}}\"\n}",
              "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v3/merchant/generate-api-key",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v3", "merchant", "generate-api-key"]
            },
            "description": "Generate (or regenerate) a merchant API key.\n\n**Auth:** existing `merchant_mobile_no` + `store_password`.\n\nThe returned `api_key` is shown only once — copy it into the `api_key` collection variable. Use it as `Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}` on the Cashback request.\n\n**Warning:** Regenerating immediately invalidates the previous key."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Success — API key generated",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v3/merchant/generate-api-key",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v3", "merchant", "generate-api-key"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [],\n  \"data\": {\n    \"api_key\": \"a3f8e2c1d5b94f7e2a1c8d3e6f9b0c4d7e2a1b5c8d3f6e9a0b4c7d2e5f8a1b4\"\n  },\n  \"code\": 200\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "422 Invalid store credentials",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"wrong\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v3/merchant/generate-api-key",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v3", "merchant", "generate-api-key"]
                }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "cookie": [],
              "body": "{\n  \"messages\": [\"Invalid store credentials.\"],\n  \"data\": null,\n  \"code\": 422\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Cashback",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Accept",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}",
                "description": "Preferred auth method. When present, merchant_mobile_no and store_password in the body are ignored. Generate a key via POST /api/v3/merchant/generate-api-key."
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"receiver_mobile_no\": \"{{customer_mobile_no}}\",\n  \"amount\": 1000,\n  \"reference_id\": \"testcashb90ack@122b\",\n  \"lang\": \"en\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v3/merchant/cash-back",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v3", "merchant", "cash-back"]
            },
            "description": "Transfer funds from your merchant wallet to a customer personal wallet as cashback or refund. Settled synchronously — the customer's balance is updated in the same response."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 Success — cashback sent",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"},
                  {"key": "Accept", "value": "application/json"}
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"merchant_mobile_no\": \"+9647712345678\",\n  \"store_password\": \"test@store123\",\n  \"receiver_mobile_no\": \"+9646666666666\",\n  \"amount\": 1000,\n  \"reference_id\": \"testcashb90ack@122b\",\n  \"lang\": \"en\"\n}",
                  "options": {"raw": {"language": "json"}}
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v3/merchant/cash-back",
                  "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
                  "path": ["api", "v3", "merchant", "cash-back"]
                }
